---
title: Seared Provençal Steak with Three-Bean Salad
description: Herbes de Provence is floral, earthy blend of flavors from the south of France. Its signature aroma comes from dried lavender, and unexpectedly delicious addition to steak and other grilled meats. We've brightened up the traditional three-bean salad with perfectly crisp-tender beans and a light shallot vinaigrette.
